# World Cup 2026 Teletext Dashboard — environment variables
# Copy this file to .env.local and fill in your keys.
# .env.local is gitignored — never commit real API keys.

# ── Live Scores ────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
# football-data.org free tier (10 req/min, major competitions incl. World Cup)
# Sign up at https://www.football-data.org/client/register
# Competition code for FIFA World Cup: WC  (season auto-set to 2026)
VITE_FD_KEY=your_football_data_org_key_here

# ── News Headlines ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
# BBC Sport RSS is fetched via allorigins.win (free CORS proxy, no key needed).
# No configuration required — headlines load automatically.
# To swap the feed, edit CORS_PROXY / BBC_FEED constants in src/lib/liveData.ts
